---
title: Reprojected DynamicMapLayer
description: Map services published in projections other than Web Mercator (like <a href="http://sampleserver6.arcgisonline.com/arcgis/rest/services/SampleWorldCities/MapServer">this one</a>) will be reprojected on the fly automatically.  More information about Map Services can be found in the <a href="../api-reference/layers/dynamic-map-layer.html">L.esri.DynamicMapLayer</a> documentation.
layout: example.hbs
---

<div id="map"></div>

<script>
  //Initialize the map to center on Brasil
  var map = L.map('map').setView([-12.73948, -60.13659], 4);

  //Add Gray Basemap
  L.esri.basemapLayer("Gray").addTo(map);
  var dynLayer = L.esri.dynamicMapLayer({
    url: "http://sampleserver6.arcgisonline.com/arcgis/rest/services/SampleWorldCities/MapServer"
  });

  map.addLayer(dynLayer);
</script>
